to be synced up.

161
00:05:26,912 --> 00:05:29,777
Put those back on...

162
00:05:29,812 --> 00:05:31,676
Uh, he's compatible
just the way that he is.

163
00:05:31,710 --> 00:05:32,815
Does anybody
want to play with him?

164
00:05:32,849 --> 00:05:34,817
Anybody?

165
