everything's fine.

215
00:07:35,075 --> 00:07:36,835
Okay.

216
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:39,838
Ahem.

217
00:07:39,873 --> 00:07:41,081
Way to go, Connor.

218
00:07:41,115 --> 00:07:42,531
Yeah,
thanks a lot.

219
00:07:42,565 --> 00:07:43,670
