a hulky Christmas Santa doll,

233
00:08:03,206 --> 00:08:04,967
and that's popular,
you know, in the moment,

234
00:08:05,001 --> 00:08:06,865
but it doesn't stand
the test of time,

235
00:08:06,900 --> 00:08:08,833
not like the toys
that I make.

236
00:08:08,867 --> 00:08:10,179
Well,

237
00:08:10,213 --> 00:08:13,769
